title: Star Wars Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II + Mysteries of the Sith
description:
Star Wars Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II + Mysteries of the Sith

3 ISOs, ripped straight from the original discs. + Scans of the two manuals that came with the game.

Good luck installing this on a modern computer, use a Virtual Machine or program like DOSBOX to run the game. ISOs are required to play the game otherwise the sound/cutscenes will be messed up so don't delete them after installing.

I'm just a Star Wars fan that had a hard time finding a good download of this game, so I've made it easier for fellow Star Wars fans.

Have fun!
